### Task
Aggregate the codes from every role and decide which reflect **consensus**  
and which show **divergence**.

### Categorisation rules
✅ **Agreed**  
• Codes that are semantically similar **and** appear in ≥ 2 roles.  
• Merge near-synonyms and give **one short unified justification**.

⚠ **Disagreement**  
• Codes that are unique, conflicting, or differ in focus / granularity.  
• Briefly explain why each is divergent (e.g. abstraction mismatch,  
  incompatible interpretation).

### Evidence requirement
• When useful, cite the Target Text using `【L x-y】` line numbers.
if the text has no explicit line numbers, treat each sentence (delimited by ., ?, !, or ？ ！) as one line
🔒 **Total output ≤ 800 tokens**

### Output — return exactly the JSON below
```json
{
  "Agreed": [
    {
      "code": "merged_code_label_1",
      "justification": "Unified justification, citing text if helpful."
    }
    // … more agreed codes
  ],
  "Disagreed": [
    {
      "code": "unique_or_conflicting_code_1",
      "justification": "Why this code diverges."
    }
    // … more disagreed codes
  ]
}
